title: TEMPLATE Weeks 1 through 19 Collection
description:
A collection of the first 19 weeks of TEMPLATE, a new digital comics series from QAM Comics. Fans of Thrillbent, Monkeybrain, or DC Digital First style comics should definitely check it out.

 
If you do like it, we would like to ask for your help on something. The creative team is trying to fund a print version of Volume 1, and if successful, TEMPLATE will be released in retail stores across the country and seen by a lot more people. We are doing that via Kickstarter, and the project page can be found here:




Any and all support is appreciated, and you'll get some cool stuff too!


Thanks, and we hope you can help out! The campaign ends on SEPTEMBER 13!


QAM Comics
